# Limitations

The findings are based on secondary sources and may not capture all aspects of successful management. The articles reviewed are opinion-based and may reflect the biases of the authors. Additionally, the context in which these traits are applied can vary significantly across different industries and organizational cultures. Further empirical research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of successful management practices.